strings: <voice_0x01001C79><se_high>Princess Medea: ...After everything you did, <hero>, after defeating Dhoulmagus, I'm still cursed?
<voice_0x01001C7A><se_high>Princess Medea: So what will we do now?

<voice_0x01001C7C><se_high>Princess Medea: I heard that Jessica disappeared.
Do you have any idea where she went?
I hope she's all right.
